To compile TerraView Hidro Plugin is necessary has 
the Boost library over ./Hidro directory

./Hidro/boost

The version from Boost used to build Hidro Plugin is
1_37_0. Boost library can be download from
http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_37_0/libs/graph/doc/index.html

